# Your SafetyCulture API token goes here (or, when hosted, in the host's
# Environment settings — never commit the real token to a repo).
# Generate one in SafetyCulture: Organization name (bottom-left) >
# Integrations > API tokens > create a SERVICE USER token.
SC_API_TOKEN=

# Optional — the host sets this automatically; only change for local runs.
# PORT=3000
